Depletion (SSB relative to unfished SSB given current recruitment dynamics) all projected years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

Depletion (SSB relative to unfished SSB given current recruitment dynamics) all projected years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

LD

Arguments

MSE
An object of class MSE

Format

An object of class PM of length 1.

Value

a matrix with n Management procedures (MSE@nMP) and nsim (MSE@nsim) columns from MSE

Examples

loadABT()
